  "title": "Commercial Operations Executive [WCNH]",
  "description": "<p><p>Handled several <strong>interior fit-out projects concurrently</strong>, ensuring completion within scheduled timelines and required quality benchmarks.</p></p><p><p>Acted as the <strong>key liaison for clients</strong>, providing regular updates, managing expectations, and maintaining strong client relationships throughout the project duration.</p></p><p><p>Took full responsibility for <strong>project delivery</strong>, overseeing planning, coordination, execution, monitoring, and final project handover.</p></p><p><p>Worked closely with <strong>in-house designers, external consultants, contractors, and suppliers</strong> to ensure smooth coordination and execution of works.</p></p><p><p>Examined <strong>design drawings and technical specifications</strong> to ensure compliance with project requirements and industry standards.</p></p><p><p>Ensured all works complied with <strong>brand standards, statutory regulations, and contractual obligations</strong>.</p></p><p><p>Prepared and updated <strong>project timelines, cost plans, and progress reports</strong> for internal management and clients.</p></p><p><p>Led <strong>site coordination meetings</strong>, monitored construction progress, and addressed on-site issues efficiently.</p></p><p><p>Oversaw <strong>procurement processes</strong>, materials coordination, and delivery scheduling to align with project schedules.</p></p><p><p>Proactively identified <strong>project risks</strong>, implemented corrective actions, and ensured adherence to <strong>quality and safety requirements</strong>.<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p></p>",
